       "     'ts': '1539889002.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'ec1613ff-e170-4a80-bdca-34a68ac81d77',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Hi! I am Apiza, a virtual assistant built to help you navigate the Allegro API. How can I help you?',\n",
