       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'I was able to find an example that may answer your question:\\n```\\nenum MYKEYS {\\n   KEY_UP, KEY_DOWN, KEY_LEFT, KEY_RIGHT\\n};```',\n",
