       "  'chatlog': {'ok': True,\n",
       "   'messages': [{'client_msg_id': '045d5e53-8532-4ed7-ad96-5e42694db41c',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Are you interested in al_draw_textf?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539985149.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'f3cc5240-d5db-44f3-bc9b-190d14bdbe31',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'How do you draw an ALLEGRO_FONT instance?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539985044.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '2f305ef0-e3bf-4686-a5c6-c631c4bfcc86',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': \"ALLEGRO_FONT is a handle identifying any kind of font. Usually you will create it with al_load_font which supports loading all kinds of TrueType fonts supported by the FreeType library. If you instead pass the filename of a bitmap file, it will be loaded with al_load_bitmap and a font in Allegro's bitmap font format will be created from it with al_grab_font_from_bitmap.\",\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984982.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'b56287c1-77d5-4a63-b770-234eaa09a572',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'How to draw an ALLEGRO_FONT to backbuffer?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984947.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'b62715b2-b3a9-4d99-841f-802928f11944',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Allegro render ttf font',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984922.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '81fd8bdc-6e81-44fa-b3fe-8eb5f1480fbc',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_init_ttf_addon call this after al_init_font_addon to make al_load_font recognize \".ttf\" and other formats supported by al_load_ttf_font. Returns true on success, false on failure.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984749.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '7b62fc9e-ab7c-41fb-aa36-401b9ea7af9d',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Do I need to initialize allegro for ttf fonts?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984692.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '26b5b34e-e4ff-4ff9-aaec-6130cd637998',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_load_bitmap_font_flags like al_load_bitmap_font but additionally takes a flags parameter which is a bitfield containing a combination of the following:\\nALLEGRO_NO_PREMULTIPLIED_ALPHA\\nThe same meaning as for al_load_bitmap_flags.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984496.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'a0111d51-c340-4590-bd68-9492e9839586',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'List al_load_bitmap_font_flags',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984445.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '42973e89-95bb-4c44-afe0-82ca73f2353b',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'ALLEGRO_FONT *al_load_font(char const *filename, int size, int flags)',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984428.000200'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'd8a95543-4397-4531-915b-9fb636bdd00e',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'function signature for al_load_font',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984419.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '1a1e7dc8-aa67-46d7-aa6d-a1a4d69b85c9',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_load_font loads a font from disk. This will use al_load_bitmap_font_flags if you pass the name of a known bitmap format, or else al_load_ttf_font.\\nThe flags parameter is passed through to either of those functions. Bitmap and TTF fonts are also affected by the current bitmap flags at the time the font is loaded.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984389.000200'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '1556c5f2-0bd5-4759-9a3b-31a16b9bee4c',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'How do you load a font in allegro?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539984364.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '962c6d91-184c-466c-b61f-5c18ab043e86',\n",
