       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_play_sample plays a sample on one of the sample instances created by al_reserve_samples. Returns true on success, false on failure. Playback may fail because all the reserved sample instances are currently used.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539983861.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '0da3e05d-e009-40c5-9333-5efde34318f4',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Why is al_play_sample() returning false?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539983809.000100'},\n",
