       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'ALLEGRO_SAMPLE *al_load_sample(const char *filename)',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539982671.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '334c3b63-8bb7-4124-8b7f-f0c352769f36',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Function signature for al_load_sample()',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJ7XQ0P5',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539982662.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '78a29ffc-1c19-4617-827e-3e8f8c6a0d4c',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_load_sample loads a few different audio file formats based on their extension.\\nNote that this stores the entire file in memory at once, which may be time consuming. To read the file as it is needed, use al_load_audio_stream.\\nReturns the sample on success, NULL on failure.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1539982621.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'c04e6c03-6f50-46cc-8e1d-385d7fa1db03',\n",
