       "    {'client_msg_id': '171bb14a-3d28-4252-8568-09db9c89842a',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'show me source code for al_load_ttf_font_stretch_f',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJL9AM7U',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540052200.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'e534e150-9062-4334-92de-47231c6b09f6',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Here is the source code for `al_load_ttf_font_stretch`:\\n```\\n/* Function: al_load_ttf_font_stretch\\n */\\nALLEGRO_FONT *al_load_ttf_font_stretch(char const *filename, int w, int h,\\n   int flags)\\n{\\n   ALLEGRO_FILE *f;\\n   ALLEGRO_FONT *font;\\n   ASSERT(filename);\\n\\n   f = al_fopen(filename, \"rb\");\\n   if (!f) {\\n      ALLEGRO_ERROR(\"Unable to open file for reading: %s\\\\n\", filename);\\n      return NULL;\\n   }\\n\\n   /* The file handle is owned by the function and the file is usually only\\n    * closed when the font is destroyed, in case Freetype has to load data\\n    * at a later time.\\n    */\\n   font = al_load_ttf_font_stretch_f(f, filename, w, h, flags);\\n\\n   return font;\\n}\\n```',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540052170.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'bce124df-c15c-416f-aac4-8f7a1d7efff7',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'show me source code for al_load_ttf_font_stretch',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJL9AM7U',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540052157.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '5f942865-aba6-4d64-94c6-789ddeff003e',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Here is the source code for `al_load_ttf_font`:\\n```\\n/* Function: al_load_ttf_font\\n */\\nALLEGRO_FONT *al_load_ttf_font(char const *filename, int size, int flags)\\n{\\n   return al_load_ttf_font_stretch(filename, 0, size, flags);\\n}\\n```',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540052052.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '14ccc448-13f3-4bd2-a940-cfc822279e17',\n",
