       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': \"I'm sorry, I'm not sure how to answer that question.\",\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540051917.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'bfb377c8-0663-4870-aa5a-83ab9e7b5088',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'what are the reasons al_load_ttf_font fails?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJL9AM7U',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540051857.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '0cc00b1c-671c-4e71-a0ba-35b2a9448b42',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Here is the documentation for `al_load_ttf_font`:\\n\\n```\\nLoads a TrueType font from a file using the FreeType library. Quoting from the FreeType FAQ this means support for many different font formats:\\n\\nTrueType, OpenType, Type1, CID, CFF, Windows FON/FNT, X11 PCF, and others\\n\\nThe size parameter determines the size the font will be rendered at, specified in pixels. The standard font size is measured in units per EM, if you instead want to specify the size as the total height of glyphs in pixels, pass it as a negative value.\\n\\n    Note: If you want to display text at multiple sizes, load the font multiple times with different size parameters.\\n\\nThe following flags are supported:\\n\\n    ALLEGRO_TTF_NO_KERNING - Do not use any kerning even if the font file supports it.\\n\\n    ALLEGRO_TTF_MONOCHROME - Load as a monochrome font (which means no anti-aliasing of the font is done).\\n\\n    ALLEGRO_TTF_NO_AUTOHINT - Disable the Auto Hinter which is enabled by default in newer versions of FreeType. Since: 5.0.6, 5.1.2\\n\\nSee also: al_init_ttf_addon, al_load_ttf_font_f\\n```',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540051596.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '159a27e5-d38f-4300-87a7-c3b89cf6893a',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'show me man page for  al_load_ttf_font',\n",
       "     'user': 'UDJL9AM7U',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540051542.000100'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'a069d988-72c7-4df6-8378-b940b7b91924',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Here is an example of drawing text:\\n\\n<https://wiki.allegro.cc/index.php?title=Allegro_5_Tutorial/Addons/Fonts>',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1540050764.000100'},\n",
