       "     'text': 'I believe the assertion comes from this function defined in src/keybdnu.c:\\n\\n\\n/* Function: al_is_keyboard_installed\\n */\\nbool al_is_keyboard_installed(void)\\n{\\n   return (new_keyboard_driver ? true : false);\\n}',\n",
