       "    {'client_msg_id': '8b918950-f540-4f1d-9c83-4cc0977b8b67',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': \"What does mean  al_get_keyboard: Assertion `new_keyboard_driver' failed.\",\n",
