       "     'text': 'rotate a bitmap?',\n",
       "     'user': 'UF6GJF0RE',\n",
       "     'ts': '1546709777.027800'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '290433f8-6935-4e24-84e5-02347a6ce1c6',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'void al_draw_scaled_bitmap(ALLEGRO_BITMAP *bitmap,\\n   float sx, float sy, float sw, float sh,\\n   float dx, float dy, float dw, float dh, int flags)',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1546709477.027600'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'c6223720-c9ad-4ac1-b5a2-7703dcc154ac',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'The method draws a scaled version of the given bitmap to the target bitmap.\\n\\t•\\tsx - source x\\n\\t•\\tsy - source y\\n\\t•\\tsw - source width\\n\\t•\\tsh - source height\\n\\t•\\tdx - destination x\\n\\t•\\tdy - destination y\\n\\t•\\tdw - destination width\\n\\t•\\tdh - destination height\\n\\t•\\tflags - same as for al_draw_bitmap\\nSee al_draw_bitmap for a note on restrictions on which bitmaps can be drawn where.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1546709471.027400'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': 'c06f920f-bae0-4c03-9794-0f8b1cf7c438',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'yes',\n",
