       "    {'client_msg_id': '30ffb147-7cce-4d84-a0da-e853ae1f9e73',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'void al_wait_for_event(ALLEGRO_EVENT_QUEUE *queue, ALLEGRO_EVENT *ret_event)',\n",
