       "    {'client_msg_id': 'feb51aa7-213d-44e7-9469-e64d9a844acc',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'al_wait_for_event waits until the event queue specified is non-empty. If ret_eventis not NULL, the first event in the queue will be copied into ret_event and removed from the queue. If ret_event is NULL the first event is left at the head of the queue.',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
