       "    {'client_msg_id': 'dd3ad64f-e0ff-4f33-ae78-f690d97c7b7a',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'I believe allegro5 has predefined enum values for keycodes. For instance, you could compare ev.keyboard.keycode == ALLEGRO_KEY_UP',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
