       "    {'client_msg_id': 'c4ff68ea-0b02-4ed6-a88d-20b6deb51345',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': \"I'm not sure about that. I was able to find that the known host file is in ~/.ssh/known_hosts on Unix.\",\n",
