       "    {'client_msg_id': '85681f87-d2bb-4913-9ac7-0e9029980438',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'It looks like there are several possible SSH keys. Some examples are \"ssh-rsa,ssh-dss,ecdh-sha2-nistp256\".',\n",
