       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': \"ssh_channel_open_forward() takes a long time and doesn't return any output.  Is this normal?  Is there a way to set a timeout?\",\n",
       "     'user': 'UBYEHEP0E',\n",
       "     'ts': '1532649427.000115'},\n",
