       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'To free an SSH session, try:\\nvoid ssh_free\\t(\\tssh_session \\tsession\\t)\\n\\nDescription\\nDeallocate a SSH session handle.\\n\\nParameters\\nsession: The SSH session to free.\\n\\nSee also\\nssh_disconnect()\\nssh_new()',\n",
