       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'To connect to a host, try using the command:\\nint ssh_connect\\t(\\tssh_session \\tsession\\t)\\n\\nDescription\\nConnect to the ssh server.\\n\\nParameters\\nsession: The ssh session to connect.\\n\\nReturns\\nSSH_OK on success, SSH_ERROR on error.\\nSSH_AGAIN, if the session is in nonblocking mode, and call must be done again.\\n\\nSee also\\nssh_new()\\nssh_disconnect()',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
       "     'ts': '1532646702.000049'},\n",
       "    {'client_msg_id': '96adc7dc-526e-4329-a88d-7c57865c2601',\n",
       "     'type': 'message',\n",
