       "     'type': 'message',\n",
       "     'text': 'Here is a struct definition that might help:\\n\\n```\\nstruct ssh_buffer_struct {\\n    char *data;\\n    uint32_t used;\\n    uint32_t allocated;\\n    uint32_t pos;\\n};\\n\\n```',\n",
