       "     'text': 'Here is a function that might help:\\n\\n```\\nssh_channel ssh_channel_new\\t(\\tssh_session \\tsession\\t)\\n\\nDescription\\nAllocate a new channel.\\n\\nParameters\\nsession: The ssh session to use.\\n\\nReturns\\nA pointer to a newly allocated channel, NULL on error.\\n\\n```',\n",
