       "     'text': 'Here is a function that might help:\\n\\n```\\nssh_session ssh_channel_get_session\\t(\\tssh_channel \\tchannel\\t)\\n\\nDescription\\nRecover the session in which belongs a channel.\\n\\nParameters\\nchannel: The channel to recover the session from.\\n\\nReturns\\nThe session pointer.\\n\\n\\n```',\n",
       "     'user': 'UB659D0FM',\n",
